Our #rewards (#income, #salary, #wages, #profit, #benefits ) in #life is always in direct proportion to the quality of our #contribution, our #service to the #world we live in. 
The #money you are paid by your #company/ employer to work will be in direct #relation to the #need of what you do, your #ability to do it, and the #degree of #difficulty involved in replacing you.

So if you want more #income then you have to be more, you have to #offer more. There is really no gimmick or get #rich quick #scheme that can safe you. You can't have a #million dollar dream with a hundred #dollar work #ethic. You get what you already are/ give in exchange for what you want or need.......#simple.
